# -famous-paintings-sql-project-
Complete Data Cleaning, Standardisation, ERD Design & Analysis using BigQuery

#  Overview  
This project demonstrates a **full end-to-end SQL workflow** on a Famous Paintings dataset using **Google BigQuery**.

It includes:
- Data Cleaning  
- Data Standardisation  
- Data Validation  
- Relationship Modelling  
- Entityâ€“Relationship Diagram (ERD)  
- Advanced SQL Analytical Insights  
- GitHub Project Documentation  

**Author:** Towhidul  

