# Analysis Questions & Insights

All analysis SQL files are in:


Some questions answered:

# Artwork & Museum Insights
- Paintings not displayed in any museum  
- Museums without any paintings  
- Museums open every single day  
- Museum with longest opening hours  
- Country with 5th highest number of paintings  

# Artist Insights
- Top 5 most popular artists  
- Artists with paintings in multiple countries  
- Artist with most Portrait paintings outside USA  

# Painting Insights
- Top 10 most popular subjects  
- Most expensive & least expensive painting  
- Paintings priced above regular price  
- Paintings priced below 50% of regular price  

# Canvas & Product Insights
- Most expensive canvas size  
- 3 least popular canvas sizes  
- Styles with highest popularity  
- Museums with most popular painting style  


# How to Run the Project

1. Open **Google BigQuery**
2. Run all SQL files in `cleaning_queries/` to generate cleaned tables.
3. Run any SQL file in `analysis_queries/` to get insights.
4. View the ERD to understand the relationships.


